Class WebUITab

  • Object
    • org.apache.spark.ui.WebUITab
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SparkUITab

    public abstract class WebUITab
extends Object
    A tab that represents a collection of pages. The prefix is appended to the parent address to form a full path, and must not contain slashes.
